							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm col-md-6 col-lg ftco-animate">
					<div class="product">
						<a href="#" class="img-prod"><img class="img-fluid"
							src="/resources/images/blog.png" alt="Colorlib Template"></a>
